function submitSearchForm(mobile) {
  if(mobile) {
    if($('#search-header-box-mobile').val())
      document.forms['search-form-mobile'].submit();
  }
  else {
    if($('#search-header-box').val())
      document.forms['search-form'].submit();
  }
}

$('#search-form').submit(function(e) {
   if (!$('#search-header-box').val()) {
       e.preventDefault();
   }
});

$('#search-form-mobile').submit(function(e) {
   if (!$('#search-header-box-mobile').val()) {
       e.preventDefault();
   }
});
